---more\ngas-rich and prone to instabilities than local spirals---which could also lead\nto gas inflows without the need of bars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Sep 2014 20:00:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 9 Feb 2015 13:42:47 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 26 Feb 2015 13:43:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-22"}
