 nature, thereby allowing us to make a clear-cut\nprediction. These results are quite important in view of the planned VHE\ndetectors like the CTA, HAWK and HiSCORE.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Sep 2014 07:46:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-09-11"}
